text: Trichophantasis grandicollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1967.BioLib.cz - Trichophantasis grandicollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phantasini Category:Beetles described in 1967
